A seed dibber is used to plant seeds in Farming patches. Up to 100 can be stored with Tool leprechauns near Farming patches.

They can be purchased from farming shops or any farmer that protects patches. An unlimited amount can be taken from a tool store 5.

A seed dibber is required the quests: Forgettable Tale..., My Arm's Big Adventure, Garden of Tranquillity and A Tail of Two Cats.
